- [x] B023 loop-capture bugs fixed in blockchain-node
- [ ] API-key auth fails closed in production (no `APP_ENV=dev` bypass)
- [ ] No PEM private keys committed to repo
- [ ] Secret scanning blocks CI on findings
- [ ] `settings.validate_secrets()` called at startup
- [ ] SQLModel `__table_args__` duplication fixed
- [ ] `tests/unit` passes (or expectations match implementation)
- [ ] Mypy CI enforces "no new errors on changed files"
- [ ] CI installs project, not just standalone tools
- [ ] Router duplicates eliminated in coordinator `main.py`
- [ ] `/docs`, `/redoc`, `/_debug/routes` disabled in production
- [ ] No default secrets outside test contexts
- [ ] MD5 removed from cache-key generation
- [ ] Smoke test for app imports passes in CI

